{"item_id":"a751d81226:0","text":"《青春变形记》© Disney/Pixar"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:1","text":"Hair & Fur Presets"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:2","text":"RenderMan 现在随附实用的毛发和皮毛预设，请在 Preset Browser 中查看。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:3","text":"LamaHairChiang 是 Pixar 生产中使用的 Pixar Chiang 毛发着色器的可分层版本。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:4","text":"它基于"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:5","text":"Disney Animation Studios 的研究"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:6","text":"并相较于"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:7","text":"PxrMarschnerHair"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:8","text":" 提供了多项改进，包括更好的收敛、更逼真的管状高光响应，以及经过重新映射的颜色；在不同粗糙度水平下，它更接近所选颜色。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:9","text":"提示和技巧"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:10","text":"要将它与 "}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:22","text":"PxrHairColor"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:12","text":" 一起使用，请确保将 "}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:25","text":"R Specular Color"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:14","text":" 属性设置为白色，并只通过 "}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:15","text":"Color TT"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:17","text":"如果使用 "}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:19","text":"，请禁用 "}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:20","text":"Remap TT Color"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:21","text":"，因为 "}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:23","text":"已经会重新映射输入颜色。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:24","text":"SPECULAR"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:26","text":"R 波瓣的 Specular 颜色。它表示光线遇到毛发曲线时的第一次反弹。此波瓣"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:27","text":"的颜色通常应为 WHITE；其响应与表面着色器的电介质材质一致。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:28","text":"在特殊情况下，可能会根据美术指导给此波瓣染色；请谨慎操作。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:29","text":"TT Specular Color"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:30","text":"TT 波瓣的 Specular 颜色。完整 Chiang 组件的主要反照率。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:31","text":"考虑毛发体积中的可见性和反弹，默认值 0.4 大致对应中灰。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:32","text":"Remap TT"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:33","text":"Color：重新映射透射颜色，使最终皮毛颜色看起来更接近实际颜色。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:34","text":"Primary Roughness"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:35","text":"R 的纵向 Roughness（以度为单位）"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:36","text":"Transmit Roughness"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:37","text":"TT 的纵向 Roughness（以度为单位）"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:38","text":"Secondary Roughness"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:39","text":"TRT 的纵向 Roughness（以度为单位）"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:41","text":"Azimuthal Roughness"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:42","text":"Specular Offset"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:43","text":"锥角偏移（以度为单位）。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:44","text":"Refractive Index"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:45","text":"折射率。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:46","text":"R Specular Gain"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:47","text":"毛发高光 R 波瓣的 Gain。它类似透明涂层，其中高光"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:48","text":"相当锐利而有光泽，通常不带颜色。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:49","text":"TT Specular Gain"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:50","text":"毛发高光 TT 波瓣的 Gain。这是一种透射类型（折射）"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:51","text":"高光，并带有一定体积衰减。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:52","text":"TRT Specular Gain"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:53","text":"毛发高光 TRT 波瓣的 Gain。这是更粗糙且带颜色的高光。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:54","text":"TRRT Specular Gain"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:55","text":"残余能量的 Gain，也是一种高光能量。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:56","text":"GLOBALS"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:58","text":"Shadow Color"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:59","text":"ADVANCED"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:60","text":"Specular Mollification"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:61","text":"可改善收敛，但可能改变皮毛外观。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:62","text":"R Specular Lobe Name"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:63","text":"定义可在 LPE AOV 中用于高光 R 波瓣的名称。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:64","text":"TT Specular Lobe Name"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:65","text":"定义可在 LPE AOV 中用于高光 TT 波瓣的名称。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:66","text":"TRT Specular Lobe Name"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:67","text":"定义可在 LPE AOV 中用于高光 TRT 波瓣的名称。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:68","text":"Diffuse Lobe Name"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:69","text":"定义可在 LPE AOV 中用于 Diffuse 波瓣的名称。"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:70","text":"Matte"}
{"item_id":"a751d81226:71","text":"定义 matte 系统可使用的名称，用于将此波瓣在最终材质中的权重输出为 AOV。"}
